{"tid":1270744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"始終都係要流血","createTime":"2019-07-01T02:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T06:12:50.000Z","uid":134912,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"259d0d5104a35fdd34b19cf2d14018082c1c5563","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"我哋頂咗咁耐，就黎變雨革2.0啦，你班大嗌和平既係咪保證呢個信口雌黃，腐敗不堪既政府會改變？<br />\n我地忍咗20年啦，儲民意儲咗咁耐，死咗咁多人<br />\n，俾藍絲辱罵我地，政府照樣唔理你地，照冷處理，幾時先可以拎得番我地應得既野？<br />\n成日話咩要拉攏中間派，嗰班騎牆派見你過火少少就變身做藍絲，唔拉都擺啦<br />\n我地已經用和平手段俾世界睇到我地既質素，但政府堅持寸步不讓，仲得寸進尺，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個唔係就係合理勇武既理由咩？ 仲要驚咩俾世界所指責？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人幾時先明白，大家一齊團結勇武到尾先會勝利</span></span>，先係最保障各位義士安全既方法，先係報答眾烈士捨身取義既精神？<br />\n<br />\n只有勝利，先可以拯救被補既義士，成王敗寇，先可以取消暴動定性，先可以正名為革命！"},{"pid":"e55aac54b567c9a5c332d1827a182b787fe3eb48","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4bc97b6ab40de914157ca0b3bddd9340b1fb171","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"78c58983366dde332b01dc23b7f5d255043ae509","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ae811e4129801a9dc38f93874bc8cd6ab30cd7dc","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20cbb549db7a1dddd89bd490f6e0539480307a99","tid":1270744,"uid":134912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d334a775d010aa17343abc49753bca32298aeb4b","tid":1270744,"uid":186849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7853449055500bd468b0c8afda87f46c5a822a7","tid":1270744,"uid":5721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor